You may continue using this version of CheckValve on your device, but if you wish to use any future versions, please upgrade to a newer device or Android version.

This feature requires the use of a CheckValve Chat Relay. The Chat Relay receives log messages from the game server and relays player chats to CheckValve. If you do not currently have a Chat Relay, it's easy to set one up and start using this feature.

Documentation and downloads can be found at the following URL:

https://sites.google.com/site/checkvalveapp/chatrelay
